**Resolution:**
I eventually got it to work. Here is the final code:gayguides %>% 
  filter(state == "SC", Year >= 1970 & Year <= 1975) %>%
  group_by(city, Year) %>%
  summarize(location_count = n(), na.rm = TRUE) %>%
  group_by(city) %>%
  summarize(avg_locations = mean(location_count))
```

**What I learned:**
I learned how to use these tools to find the average location for a certain year span.

